```{r}
library(rEDM)
library(tidyverse)
library(googlesheets4)

library(zoo)
```

```{r}

TS <- read_sheet('https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1vX03QRkc0E1Pc0Aea2jMu9E3rOWWrQo0jC5HckOo1qs/edit?usp=sharing')


```
```{r}

TS$Date<-as.Date(with(TS,paste(year,month,day,sep="-")),"%Y-%m-%d")

```

```{r}
TS <- TS[-c(2:4)] #remove columns
```

```{r}
write.csv(TS, file = "TS.csv")
```
